    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find for any discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in showroom state, smelling fresh and showing no signs of wear on the premium upholstery. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and stored in a climate-controlled garage. Every feature, from the advanced electronics to the smooth-shifting transmission, functions exactly as it did the day it was manufactured. This is a collector-grade example that offers a like-new driving experience.",
